OL,4,Cneeded to 'scratch surface' of crime
OL,6,FLawyers are calling for a dedicated
OL,7,Fdrugs and alcohol court to target a
OL,8,Fcycle of crime blighting generations
OL,9,Fof people on Teesside.
OL,11,FLeading family law barristers and
OL,12,Fjudges are supporting a bid to create
OL,13,Fthe specialist court to try and break
OL,14,Fwhat they describe as the
OL,15,F'generational cycle' of crime borne
OL,16,Ffrom addiction.
