OL,6,FThe South Durham and Cleveland Family
OL,7,FJustice Board held a conference in
OL,8,FMiddlesbrough last week which heard
OL,9,Fhow children and young people are
OL,10,Foften recruited into crime gangs to
OL,11,Ffuel the supply of street drugs.
OL,13,FThe Cleveland Police area has one of
OL,14,Fthe highest rates of drug crime in
OL,15,FEngland, with the force recently
OL,16,Flaunching a 'Matrix' policing unit
OL,17,Fwhich is dedicated to tackling serious
OL,18,Fcrime often linked to drugs.
