OL,3,CSpecialist drugs and alcohol court
OL,4,Cneeded to 'scratch surface' of crime
OL,6,FA specialist drugs and alcohol court
OL,7,Fis run by professionals with vast
OL,8,Fexperience of how to support young
OL,9,Fpeople out of the drugs trade, rather
OL,10,Fthan punishing them only to see them
OL,11,Fre-offend.
OL,13,FManchester is one of the few areas in
OL,14,Fthe country to have one.
OL,16,FIt is hoped the creation of a court on
OL,17,FTeesside will help to reduce the crime
OL,18,Frate and offer young people new
OL,19,Fopportunities.
